divs: sighting detailsi was observing a very strange looking cloud in the evening sky in ainsworth, ia that wasn't moving. afterwards when i looked at the photos it looked liked this small ufo came shooting out of it. i'm not sure what it was but i've never seen a cloud like this and i have taken a lot of weather photo's. i may be nothing but i wanted to post it just in case someone else has noticed anything in the area besides corn and cows. *(wit's initials deleted--cms\sg).
trends: There have been no other sightings in Ainsworth
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: Captured small round UFO near strange looking cloud
